name: THE MOON
description: FROM MY FIRST ORACLE DECK: INITIATION / The Moon is the subconscious mind. It's how you react emotionally & instinctively in life. It influences your feelings, your habits, your mood and your receptivity. It's the root of your feminine energy & maternal instincts. The moon is commonly associated with the mother figure, conditioning & childhood. It's the nurturing & caring side of the self. ⠀
